{"tid":1603834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[9.29]策略分析","createTime":"2019-09-29T19:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T19:31:31.000Z","uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d8d5334c47b2ba1f37e5b5aaf576251fcf3b48c","tid":1603834,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:09:17.000Z","msg":"其實今次好明顯係黑警set好曬陷阱等你<br />\n入黎<br />\n<br />\n而暗門其實好多，大廈好多防火門如果set幾隊人係周圍防火梯一定拉到人除非全部人都唔退後，大家都知係冇可能<br />\n<br />\n咁不如臨時轉場，文宣同之後遊行都宣傳啲人入曬同一個tg減少和理非，手足落單<br />\n<br />\n而一轉場黑警部署將會完全亂曬，和理非可以安全啲，勇武都可以有時間準備同唔洗因為黑警rb比人捉"},{"pid":"c5922ae275023dba5cb7aa37fee989d48882ef3e","tid":1603834,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:12:13.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"c4d4bc8257803445e775a5fa8d195e020f97ff5b","tid":1603834,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:12:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"002816cdc59fbbfabece61303b53659d1480ba64","tid":1603834,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:12:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a23867cc7b57fd66bffad677e75b6beec6828187","tid":1603834,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:12:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23a0ba02a9158ea06c279341bb1f3d2e1a4f2601","tid":1603834,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:13:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e61cf68ccacd6984b26605597e0f9805180f00a5","tid":1603834,"uid":314909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:13:12.000Z","msg":"唔係想唔想轉場嘅問題，係無鐵轉唔倒"},{"pid":"30417d9292d127018161e2e8f68a3a7f4ceb7ff4","tid":1603834,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e61cf68ccacd6984b26605597e0f9805180f00a5","tid":1603834,"uid":314909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:13:12.000Z","msg":"唔係想唔想轉場嘅問題，係無鐵轉唔倒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:14:33.000Z","msg":"唔係開始左之後先轉，而係遊行開始前一兩個鐘先再